# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║                                                                              ║
# ║   🚨🚨🚨 DO NOT ADD RANDOM SHIT HERE 🚨🚨🚨                                   ║
# ║                                                                              ║
# ║   This .gitignore is CURATED. Do not add entries without understanding      ║
# ║   WHY they should be ignored. Every entry here serves a purpose.            ║
# ║                                                                              ║
# ║   BEFORE ADDING ANYTHING:                                                   ║
# ║   1. Ask yourself: "Is this actually generated/temporary/sensitive?"        ║
# ║   2. If it's evidence, logs, or investigation data - IT SHOULD BE TRACKED   ║
# ║   3. Random IDE configs, personal prefs - CHECK WITH USER FIRST             ║
# ║   4. If in doubt, DON'T ADD IT. Ask.                                        ║
# ║                                                                              ║
# ║   This file exists because of systematic security breakdown incidents.      ║
# ║   See: POST-LOCKDOWN-REPORT-2026-03-23.md for full context.                 ║
# ║                                                                              ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

# =============================================================================
# PARSED OUTPUT - Too large for repo, regenerated from source
# =============================================================================
logs/*.json
!logs/.gitkeep

# =============================================================================
# PYTHON - Standard build artifacts (NEVER ignore .py source files)
# =============================================================================
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.Python
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
dist/
build/

# =============================================================================
# VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENTS - Local dev only, not repo content
# =============================================================================
venv/
env/
.env

# =============================================================================
# IDE - Personal config only, NOT shared workspace settings
# =============================================================================
# Track: .vscode/mcp.json (shared MCP config)
# Ignore: Personal local settings
.vscode/settings.json
.vscode/launch.json
.vscode/tasks.json
.vscode/extensions.json
.vscode/*.code-workspace
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# =============================================================================
# OS - Filesystem metadata garbage
# =============================================================================
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# =============================================================================
# TEMP FILES - Ephemeral, regenerate on demand
# =============================================================================
*.tmp
*.bak

# =============================================================================
# ⚠️ DO NOT ADD BELOW THIS LINE WITHOUT EXPLICIT USER APPROVAL ⚠️
# =============================================================================
